=== 蒙鲁日枪击案 ===
1月8日，一名叫阿梅迪·库利巴利的32岁塞內加爾男子，在巴黎南部郊区[[蒙鲁日|蒙鲁日]][[和平大道|和平大道]]和皮埃尔·布罗索莱大道的交界处，开枪打死一名警察。一名清道夫也在袭击中严重受伤。消息人士表示，库利巴利跟袭击查理周刊的枪手，隸屬於同一個聖戰組織，法国警方表示事件之间存在著某種關係<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.dpa-international.com/news/international/updateprofilethe-kouachi-brothers-and-amedy-coulibaly-comrades-in-terrorism-a-43827912.html|title=UPDATE PROFILE The Kouachi brothers and Amedy Coulibaly: comrades in terrorism|publisher=dpa-international.com|date=2015-01-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110022859/http://www.dpa-international.com/news/international/updateprofilethe-kouachi-brothers-and-amedy-coulibaly-comrades-in-terrorism-a-43827912.html|archivedate=2015年1月10日}}</ref>。

===文森門脅持案===
阿梅迪·库利巴利其後於1月9日闖入巴黎東部[[文森門|文森門]]（Porte de Vincennes）一家猶太人超市，劫持多名人質。大批全副武裝的警員立刻封鎖了超市附近地區，而警方的直升機也在有關地區上空盤旋。<ref>{{cite news |title=巴黎超市圍捕槍手：警方開始突擊行動 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/01/150109_paris_shooting2_clonel |newspaper=BBC |accessdate=2015-01-09}}</ref>

==围捕行动==
枪击案發生後，法國警方立刻開展大規模搜捕行動。法國內政部長宣布在全國各地已經部署88,000名警員和安全部隊士兵。

库阿希兄弟在枪击案後，在巴黎北區的莫城街（Rue de Meaux）棄車而逃，並劫持了第二輛小汽車。<ref>{{cite news|title=巴黎槍襲十多人死傷 兇手身份被鎖定|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/01/150107_paris_shooting_update|newspaper=BBC|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111202536/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/01/150107_paris_shooting_update|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩人其後在[[埃納省|埃納省]][[維萊科特雷|維萊科特雷]]市RN2公路旁搶劫了一個加油站，獲得食物和汽油之後，繼續逃亡。<ref>{{cite news|title=雜誌社槍擊案主要疑犯據報又打劫加油站|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/01/150108_france_robber_gunmen|newspaper=BBC|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150117202626/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/01/150108_france_robber_gunmen|dead-url=no}}</ref>

警員們將搜捕重點集中在該加油站附近的幾個鄉鎮和森林地區，還將[[皮卡第|皮卡第]]區的警戒等級提到了最高程度。全副武裝的警員們，在當地挨家挨戶搜索库阿希兄弟。法國警方的[[特種部隊|特種部隊]]亦部署在該地區，裝備包括直升機。<ref>{{cite news|title=巴黎槍擊案嫌犯追捕進程|url=http://cn.tmagazine.com/culture/20150108/cc08parismap/zh-hant/|newspaper=紐約時報|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110144404/http://cn.tmagazine.com/culture/20150108/cc08parismap/zh-hant/|archive-date=2015-01-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=巴黎槍擊屠殺 追捕兇手行動進入第三天|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/01/150108_france_manhunt|newspaper=BBC|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111145623/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/01/150108_france_manhunt|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 围攻达马尔坦昂戈埃勒 ===
1月9日上午，法政府证实巴黎东北部35公里处[[塞納-馬恩省|塞納-馬恩省]]的[[达马尔坦昂戈埃勒|达马尔坦昂戈埃勒]]传出枪声和爆炸声<ref name="BBClive">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-europe-30722098|title=Charlie Hebdo attack: Manhunt – live reporting|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-01-09|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224145001/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-europe-30722098|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据报道，在交火中有多人受伤，可能有一人死亡，警方將达马尔坦昂戈埃勒重重包圍，並告誡居民，千萬不要出門<ref name="BBClive"/>。

上午9时30分左右，库阿希兄弟帶著[[卡拉什尼科夫自動步槍|AK-47突擊步槍]]與[[火箭筒|火箭筒]]逃进达马尔坦昂戈埃勒工业区，衝入标示牌印刷廠“创作发现趋势公司”的办公室（坐标：{{Coord|49.063122|2.694095|type:landmark_scale:5000}}），公司老闆卡塔拉諾（Michele Catalano）命其26岁員工勒佩爾（Lilian Lepere）到廠房後面躲避，卡塔拉諾自己留下來與库阿希兄弟周旋，這兩名槍手對卡塔拉諾很有禮貌，對話間皆稱之為「先生」。卡塔拉諾泡[[咖啡|咖啡]]招待這兩名槍手，氣氛融洽，又發現其中一人頸部流血，也幫他敷藥。正當此時，一名廠商來公司洽公，遇上這兩名槍手，其中一人表示：「我不殺無辜的平民。」並讓該廠商離去。卡塔拉諾約被挾持一個小時後，平安獲釋。勒佩爾則一直躲在廠房後的紙箱內，不斷傳[[簡訊|簡訊]]通知警察公司內的狀況，並提供两名槍手的位置、武器等資料<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1404787/paris-terror-suspects-cornered-after-car-chase|title=Paris Terror Suspects 'Ready To Die'|publisher=Sky News}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2903870/The-hostage-terrorists-didn-t-know-Print-worker-hid-box-texted-police-Charlie-Hebdo-gunmen-held-boss-captive-final-showdown.html|title=The hostage the terrorists didn't know they had: Print worker hid in cardboard box for eight hours|work=Daily Mail|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109233358/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2903870/The-hostage-terrorists-didn-t-know-Print-worker-hid-box-texted-police-Charlie-Hebdo-gunmen-held-boss-captive-final-showdown.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Yahoo! News">{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/paris-hostages-survived-hidden-fridges-beneath-sinks-031226533.html|title=Paris hostages survived hidden in fridges and beneath sinks|date=2015-01-09|work=Yahoo! News|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120175152/https://news.yahoo.com/paris-hostages-survived-hidden-fridges-beneath-sinks-031226533.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而後警方發現了库阿希兄弟的蹤跡，[[戴高乐机场|戴高乐机场]]附近10公里处因警方围攻而关闭两条飞机跑道<ref name="BBClive" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/faits-divers/prise-d-otages-dammartin-en-goele.shtml|title=Création Tendance découverte: prise d'otages à Dammartin en Goële|publisher=linternaute.com|date=2015-01-09|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109124157/http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/faits-divers/prise-d-otages-dammartin-en-goele.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。内政部长[[貝爾納·卡澤納夫|貝爾納·卡澤納夫]]呼吁警方采取行动消灭凶手。然而，该部发言人表示希望率先与嫌犯「建立对话」。官员接触了這兩名槍手，谈判在封锁区500米处一間人员安全撤出的学校内展开<ref name="BBCOP2">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-30740115 Charlie Hebdo hunt: Police surround Paris suspects] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-30740115 |date=20201201161517 }}, BBC News. Retrieved 9 January 2015.</ref>。

围困持续了八个多小时，邻近大楼下午16時30分左右至少响起三次爆炸声，库阿希兄弟被击毙，行动结束。一名法国安全官员证实，這兩名槍手“走出来开火”时被击毙。人质安然无恙<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/charlie-hebdo-attack-3-suspects-4-hostages-killed-in-separate-attacks-near-paris-1.2894956 Charlie Hebdo attack: 3 suspects, 4 hostages killed in separate attacks near Paris] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/charlie-hebdo-attack-3-suspects-4-hostages-killed-in-separate-attacks-near-paris-1.2894956 |date=20201217131452 }}, CBC News. Retrieved 9 January 2015.</ref><ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30754340 Charlie Hebdo attack: Kouachi brothers killed] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30754340 |date=20170220085422 }}, BBC News. Retrieved 9 January 2015.</ref>。现场搜出燃烧瓶和[[榴弹发射器|榴弹发射器]]等武器<ref name="Yahoo! News"/>。

=== 围攻文森门 ===
同样在1月9日，手持两把[[卡拉什尼科夫自動步槍|AK-47突擊步槍]]的库利巴利，袭击了巴黎东部[[文森门|文森门]]公园一個[[犹太|犹太]]杂货店，杀死四人，并挟持人质<ref name="BBClive" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/world/1.636178|title=Paris shooting updates / Charlie Hebdo attackers take hostage after car chase|date=2015-01-09|work=Haaretz|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2015-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110035544/http://www.haaretz.com/news/world/1.636178|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的女性帮凶推测是他的妻子哈亚特·布迈丁<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.midilibre.fr/2015/01/09/prise-d-otages-dans-une-epicerie-casher-par-un-homme-arme-porte-de-vincennes,1108461.php|title=DIRECT – Porte de Vincennes: plusieurs otages, au moins deux morts|publisher=MidiLibre.fr|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111232956/http://www.midilibre.fr/2015/01/09/prise-d-otages-dans-une-epicerie-casher-par-un-homme-arme-porte-de-vincennes,1108461.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后来证实，库利巴利也是蒙鲁日案的罪魁祸首<ref name="lemonde.fr"/>。一名目击者称：“人们在购物时，一名男子拿着[[步枪|步枪]]进来，往各个方向开枪。我趕緊跑出来。枪声持续了几秒钟」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/paris-attacks-armed-gunman-takes-hostage-in-kosher-grocery-shop-in-east-of-city-9967968.html|title=Paris attacks: Gunman and four hostages killed at kosher grocery shop as police launch assault|date=2015-01-09|work=The Independent|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427165339/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/paris-attacks-armed-gunman-takes-hostage-in-kosher-grocery-shop-in-east-of-city-9967968.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，據《[[卫报|卫报]]》报道，當時库利巴利在采访中，他表示自己「犯下的这些行为，是在捍卫『被压迫的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]』，尤其是[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]出身的，並以猶太人開設的雜貨店為目標，展開報復猶太人的行動<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/jan/09/charlie-hebdo-manhunt-kouachi-terrorist-links-live-updates#block-54b04e67e4b0461a99f13aea|title=Charlie Hebdo attack: French officials establish link between gunmen in both attacks — live|author=Matthew Weaver|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2015-01-10|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302190443/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/jan/09/charlie-hebdo-manhunt-kouachi-terrorist-links-live-updates#block-54b04e67e4b0461a99f13aea|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/09/us-france-shooting-idUSKBN0KG0Y120150109|title=French forces kill newspaper attack suspects, hostages die in second siege|work=Reuters|accessdate=2015-01-10|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924212225/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/09/us-france-shooting-idUSKBN0KG0Y120150109|dead-url=yes}}</ref>」。

库利巴利据称在围攻过程中与库阿希兄弟碰面，并告诉警方如果两兄弟受伤，他会杀害人质<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/paris-shooting-armed-man-takes-hostages-in-paris-kosher-store-20150109-12ldgt.html|title=Paris shooting: Armed man takes hostages in Paris kosher store|date=2015-01-09|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2015-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112005420/http://www.smh.com.au/world/paris-shooting-armed-man-takes-hostages-in-paris-kosher-store-20150109-12ldgt.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方攻入杂货店击毙了库利巴利<ref>[http://heavy.com/news/2015/01/amedy-coulibaly-dead-killed-jewish-hostage-france/ Amedy Coulibaly Dead: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know] {{Wayback|url=http://heavy.com/news/2015/01/amedy-coulibaly-dead-killed-jewish-hostage-france/ |date=20150118042403 }},'</ref>。15名人质获救<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/report-suspect-in-2nd-france-cop-killing-in-hostage-situation/|title=Paris hostage situation ends with gunman dead|date=2015-01-09|publisher=[[CBS_News|CBS News]]|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109152503/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/report-suspect-in-2nd-france-cop-killing-in-hostage-situation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但包括两名警察在内的多人受伤<ref name="International Business Times">{{cite web|title=Who Is Amedy Coulibaly? Paris Kosher Deli Gunman Once Worked For Coca-Cola, Was Close With Kouachi Brothers|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/who-amedy-coulibaly-paris-kosher-deli-gunman-once-worked-coca-cola-was-close-kouachi-1779242|date=2015-01-09|work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2015-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110020325/http://www.ibtimes.com/who-amedy-coulibaly-paris-kosher-deli-gunman-once-worked-coca-cola-was-close-kouachi-1779242|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 兇手 ==
=== 赛义德·库阿希 ===
[[File:Photo_identitie-Said_Kouachi.JPG|thumb]]
[[File:Chérif_Kouachi.jpg|thumb]]
'''赛义德·库阿希'''（Saïd Kouachi，1980年9月7日－2015年1月9日）和'''谢里夫·库阿希'''（Chérif Kouachi），被法国警方认定为袭击的主要嫌疑人<ref name="nytimes1">{{cite news|last1=Higgins|first1=Andrew|author2=De La Baume, Maia|title=Two Brothers Suspected in Killings Were Known to French Intelligence Services|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/08/world/two-brothers-suspected-in-killings-were-known-to-french-intelligence-services.html?_r=0|accessdate=2015-01-08|work=The New York Times|date=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107134259/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/08/world/two-brothers-suspected-in-killings-were-known-to-french-intelligence-services.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=2015-01-07 |title=Who are the Charlie Hebdo gunmen? |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2900941/Who-Charlie-Hebdo-gunmen-Islamic-fanatics-claimed-Al-Qaeda-Yemen-shooting-12-dead.html |newspaper=Daily Mail |accessdate=2015-01-08 |archive-date=2015-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108001512/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2900941/Who-Charlie-Hebdo-gunmen-Islamic-fanatics-claimed-Al-Qaeda-Yemen-shooting-12-dead.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>两人是[[阿尔及利亚|阿尔及利亚]]裔[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]，均来自[[热讷维耶|热讷维耶]]，分别为34岁和32岁。他们的父母是來自阿尔及利亚的移民<ref name="nytimes1" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/paris-shooting-two-police-officers-injured-in-assault-rifle-attack-hours-after-charlie-hebdo-killings-9964143.html|title=Paris shooting: Female police officer dead following assault rifle attack morning after Charlie Hebdo killings|work=The Independent|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109004952/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/paris-shooting-two-police-officers-injured-in-assault-rifle-attack-hours-after-charlie-hebdo-killings-9964143.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="liberation1">{{cite web|url=http://www.liberation.fr/societe/2015/01/07/un-commando-organise-et-prepare_1175841|title=Un commando organisé|work=Libération|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921063040/http://www.liberation.fr/societe/2015/01/07/un-commando-organise-et-prepare_1175841|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nbc20140107">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/paris-magazine-attack/three-suspects-named-paris-terror-attack-n281761|title=Paris Attack Suspect Dead, Two in Custody, U.S. Officials Say|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107225828/http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/paris-magazine-attack/three-suspects-named-paris-terror-attack-n281761|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两兄弟还很小就成了孤儿，而谢里夫去巴黎找赛义德前，曾被寄养于[[雷恩|雷恩]]<ref name="liberation1" />。

===谢里夫·库阿希===
'''谢里夫·库阿希'''（Chérif Kouachi，1982年11月29日－2015年1月9日），曾用名阿布·伊森（Abu Issen），是“巴茨-肖蒙网络”的骨干，[[伊拉克战争|2003年美国入侵伊拉克]]后，协助[[基地组织|基地组织]]发动圣战。22岁的他于2005年1月被捕，当时他和另一名男子正准备离开[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]统治下的[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]，躲避[[美军|美军]]“网关行动”对圣战者的打击<ref name="autogenerated1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-30722038 |title=bbc news, 9 January 2015 |access-date=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126105828/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-30722038 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2005年1月到2006年10月的监禁期间，谢里夫遇见了贾迈勒·贝格哈尔（Djamel Beghal）。贝格哈尔于2001年被判处10年有期徒刑，他曾密谋炸毁[[美国驻巴黎大使馆|美国驻巴黎大使馆]]的部分建筑<ref name="autogenerated1"/>。

谢里夫在[[巴黎十九区|巴黎的第19区]]，成为阿达佤[[清真寺|清真寺]]的伊斯蘭激进传教士法里德·本耶图（Farid Benyettou）的学生。库阿希想袭击法国的犹太目标，但本耶图告诉他法国不像伊拉克，不是“[[吉哈德|圣战]]的地方”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/01/08/europe/paris-charlie-hebdo-shooting-suspects/ |title=cnn.com 8 January 2015 |access-date=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2015-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126043049/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/01/08/europe/paris-charlie-hebdo-shooting-suspects/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年，谢里夫因為协助運送激进穆斯林到伊拉克參加[[阿布·穆萨布·扎卡维|扎卡维]]領導的基地组织伊拉克分支活動，被判定犯有恐怖主义罪，判处3年有期徒刑，其中18個月缓期執行<ref name="nytimes1" /><ref name="nbc20140107" /><ref name="que-sait-on-des-deux-suspects-recherches">{{cite web|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/attaque-contre-charlie-hebdo/article/2015/01/08/attaque-a-charlie-hebdo-que-sait-on-des-deux-suspects-recherches_4551181_4550668.html|title=Attentat à " Charlie Hebdo ": que sait-on des deux suspects recherchés ?|author=Matthieu Suc|work=Le Monde.fr|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019173430/http://www.lemonde.fr/attaque-contre-charlie-hebdo/article/2015/01/08/attaque-a-charlie-hebdo-que-sait-on-des-deux-suspects-recherches_4551181_4550668.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/charlie-hebdo-paris-shooting-three-4938044|title=Charlie Hebdo Paris shooting: Three men suspected of killing 12 in terror attack 'holed up near Belgium border'|date=2015-01-07|work=[[Daily_Mirror|Daily Mirror]]|accessdate=2015-01-07|archive-date=2015-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108001855/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/charlie-hebdo-paris-shooting-three-4938044|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他支援伊拉克叛亂的動機，源自对美国[[阿布格莱布监狱|阿布格莱布监狱]]折磨犯人的愤怒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/paris-magazine-attack/paris-attack-suspect-dead-two-custody-u-s-officials-say-n281761|title=Paris Magazine Attack|date=2015-01-07|publisher=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|accessdate=2015-01-07|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125030652/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/paris-magazine-attack/paris-attack-suspect-dead-two-custody-u-s-officials-say-n281761|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/23872546/ns/world_news-islam_in_europe/t/french-muslims-flock-iraqs-battlefields/|title=French Muslims flock to,from Iraq's Battlefields|date=2008-03-30|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=2015-01-07|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018133153/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/23872546/ns/world_news-islam_in_europe/t/french-muslims-flock-iraqs-battlefields/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年，库阿希兄弟被认为与一起协助另一名[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]斯麦因·艾特·阿里·贝勒卡西姆（Smain Ait Ali Belkacem）越狱的案子有关。然而，因缺乏证据未起诉两人。贝勒卡西姆發動了造成8人死亡的[[1995年巴黎地铁和区域快铁爆炸案|1995年巴黎地铁和区域快铁爆炸案]]<ref name="autogenerated1"/><ref>[http://m.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/suspects-in-paris-shooting-had-cache-of-arms-neighbour-says/article22372220/ theglobeandmail.com]</ref>。

