===阿梅迪·库利巴利===
'''阿梅迪·库利巴利'''（{{lang-en|Amedy Coulibaly}}，1982年2月27日－2015年1月9日），被认定是犯下文森门挾持案和蒙鲁日枪击案的枪手<ref name="lemonde.fr">[http://www.lemonde.fr/societe/article/2015/01/09/fusillade-de-montrouge-suspect-identifie-deux-nouvelles-interpellations_4552503_3224.html Le suspect de Montrouge, Amedy Coulibaly, était bien le tireur de Vincennes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/societe/article/2015/01/09/fusillade-de-montrouge-suspect-identifie-deux-nouvelles-interpellations_4552503_3224.html |date=20150109161457 }}, ''Le Monde''</ref>。他生于巴黎郊区的奥尔日河畔于维西。17岁那年，他因犯下数起枪击案和贩毒而被定罪，精神病专家为巴黎法院准备的一份报告，发现库利巴利有着“不成熟的病态人格”，“自省能力较差<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/09/amedy-coulibaly-paris-kosher-market_n_6444418.html|title=Amedy Coulibaly, Paris Kosher Market Terrorist, Had History Of Ties To Violence|date=2015-01-09|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2018-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009024119/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/09/amedy-coulibaly-paris-kosher-market_n_6444418.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。

2005年在监狱服刑期间，他遇见因武装[[抢劫|抢劫]]入狱的谢里夫·库阿希（Cherif Kouachi），跟谢里夫一同[[皈依|皈依]][[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]，並成为[[激进派|激进派]]的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]<ref name="#2">{{cite web|work=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|Daily News]]|location=New York|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/terrorist-amedy-coulibaly-met-french-prez-nicolas-sarkozy-article-1.2072074|title=Terrorist Amedy Coulibaly met former French President Nicolas Sarkozy in 2009, years before Paris murder spree|date=2015-01-09|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111071023/https://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/terrorist-amedy-coulibaly-met-french-prez-nicolas-sarkozy-article-1.2072074|dead-url=no}}</ref>。刑满释放后，他与[[哈亚特·布迈丁|哈亚特·布迈丁]]（Hayat Boumeddiene）以未被法國法律認可的宗教儀式舉行「婚禮」。<ref>{{cite web|title=From bikini babe to burka-clad jihadi fighter with a crossbow: 'Wife' of Kosher supermarket killer becomes France's most wanted woman after going on the run|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2903601/Wife-Kosher-supermarket-killer-armed-dangerous-run-police-warn.html|date=2015-01-09|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309104727/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2903601/Wife-Kosher-supermarket-killer-armed-dangerous-run-police-warn.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年7月15日，库利巴利同其他500個法國年輕人在一場關於培訓與年輕人就業的活動中会见了时任法国总统[[尼古拉·萨科齐|尼古拉·萨科齐]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3661840/amedy-coulibaly-nicolas-sarkozy/|title=Paris Attacker Met French President in 2009|date=2015-01-09|work=Time|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116184032/https://time.com/3661840/amedy-coulibaly-nicolas-sarkozy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

会见萨科齐十个月后，库利巴利因案被調查，警方搜查其公寓时，发现了240发7.62毫米步枪子弹。库利巴利声称正打算在街上出售弹药<ref name="#2"/>。早前消息表示，库利巴利是库阿希兄弟的好友<ref name="#1"/>。库利巴利和库阿希兄弟同为“巴茨肖蒙恐怖集团”的骨干，该组织名字来源于他们经常见面、给其他法裔阿尔及利亚极端分子做体能训练的[[肖蒙山丘公园|肖蒙山丘公园]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channel4.com/news/butte-chaumont-network-paris-attacks-who-did-he|title='Buttes Chaumont' network behind Paris attacks|publisher=Channel 4|date=2015-01-09|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109234953/http://www.channel4.com/news/butte-chaumont-network-paris-attacks-who-did-he|dead-url=no}}</ref>。库利巴利被认为是受到巴黎的一名伊斯兰传教士影響而變得激進，然後萌生在[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]或[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]戰鬥的念頭<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/551058/Paris-police-officer-shot-dead-named-Clarissa-Jean-Philippe|title=Shooting of Paris police officer LINKED to Charlie Hebdo massacre|work=Daily Express|date=2015-01-09|access-date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117094307/https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/551058/Paris-police-officer-shot-dead-named-Clarissa-Jean-Philippe|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年，库利巴利因协助他人[[越狱|越狱]]，被判处有期徒刑五年，库阿希兄弟也参与其中。库利巴利後來被提早释放<ref>{{cite web|title=Who Is Amedy Coulibaly? Paris Kosher Deli Gunman Once Worked For Coca-Cola, Was Close With Kouachi Brothers|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/who-amedy-coulibaly-paris-kosher-deli-gunman-once-worked-coca-cola-was-close-kouachi-1779242|date=2015-01-09|work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2015-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110020325/http://www.ibtimes.com/who-amedy-coulibaly-paris-kosher-deli-gunman-once-worked-coca-cola-was-close-kouachi-1779242|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

