== 后续 ==
=== 法国 ===
本次事件為法国本土40年以来，傷亡人数最多的一次事件，法国政府已視為[[恐怖攻擊|恐怖攻擊]]。[[巴黎|巴黎]]乃至各地的安全警戒提升至最高層級，政府投入大量軍警進行緝捕。事發之後，在巴黎東北部、南部地區傳出數起槍擊事件。7日晚，法国全境有超过10万人为恐怖事件中的遇难者祈祷，他们高举“無畏”（Not afraid）、“[[我是查理|我是查理]]”（Je suis Charlie）等标语，以支持该周刊。<ref name=guancha01>{{cite news|title=巴黎查理周刊恐袭：3名嫌犯被捕 超10万法国人示威|url=http://www.guancha.cn/europe/2015_01_08_305642_s.shtml|accessdate=2015-01-07|date=2015-01-08|archive-date=2019-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811073218/http://www.guancha.cn/europe/2015_01_08_305642_s.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>事後，歐陸各地主張[[愛國歐洲人反對西方伊斯蘭化|西方反對伊斯蘭化]]的情緒高漲<ref name=twapple01>{{cite news|title=巴黎南部女警槍擊案與周報遇襲|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150109/538812/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E8%88%87%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C|accessdate=2015-01-09|newspaper=台灣蘋果日報|date=2015年1月9日|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204507/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150109/538812/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E8%88%87%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=udn01>{{cite news|title=反伊斯蘭的恐懼 歐洲正滋長|url=http://udn.com/news/story/6809/628751|accessdate=2015-01-08|newspaper=聯合報 編譯馮克芸／綜合報導|date=2015年1月8日|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130172839/https://udn.com/news/story/6809/628751|dead-url=no}}</ref>。幸存员工宣布下周如期出刊，八页的版面是平常的一半，印刷超过以往的6万份达到100万份<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-30724863|title=Charlie Hebdo Attack: Magazine to publish next week|date=2015-01-08|publisher=BBC|access-date=2015-01-11|archive-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021020807/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-30724863|dead-url=no}}</ref>。数字媒体创新基金会向该杂志捐赠25万欧元，与法国新闻多元化基金会的捐赠相配套<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/8/7514251/charlie-hebdo-will-publish-one-million-copies-next-week-with-help|title=Charlie Hebdo will publish one million copies next week with help from Google-backed fund|author=Russell Brandom|date=2015-01-08|publisher=The Verge|access-date=2015-01-11|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117020952/http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/8/7514251/charlie-hebdo-will-publish-one-million-copies-next-week-with-help|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/french-media-raises-500000-to-keep-satirical-magazine-charlie-hebdo-open-9965576.html|title=French media raises €500,000 to keep satirical magazine Charlie Hebdo open|work=The Independent|date=2015-01-08|author=Jon Stone|accessdate=2015-01-11|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117040117/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/french-media-raises-500000-to-keep-satirical-magazine-charlie-hebdo-open-9965576.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《卫报》传媒集团出于同样原因，单独捐赠10万英镑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/01/08/updates-on-charlie-hebdo-shooting/|title=Updates on the 2nd Day of Search for Suspects in Charlie Hebdo Shooting|date=2015-01-08|work=The New York Times|access-date=2015-01-11|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312035032/https://news.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/01/08/updates-on-charlie-hebdo-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 安保 ===

袭击发生后，法国将恐怖警戒提升至最高级别，向巴黎的公共交通系统、媒体机构、宗教场所和[[埃菲尔铁塔|埃菲尔铁塔]]部署士兵。[[英国外交部|英国外交部]]警告前往巴黎的公民<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pleasance|first1=Chris|title=Soldiers on the streets: Military is brought in to protect Eiffel Tower, media offices, places of worship and public transport links as France responds to terror attack|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2900755/Soldiers-streets-Military-brought-protect-Eiffel-Tower-media-offices-places-worship-public-transport-links-France-responds-terror-attack.html|accessdate=2015-01-07|work=Daily Mail|date=2015-01-07|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031170756/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2900755/Soldiers-streets-Military-brought-protect-Eiffel-Tower-media-offices-places-worship-public-transport-links-France-responds-terror-attack.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[纽约市警察局|纽约市警察局]]下令加强位于[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]][[上东城|上东城]]法国驻纽约总领事馆的安保措施<ref name="abcnews">{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/gunmen-charlie-hebdo-attack-called-victims-names-shot/story?id=28050771|title=Gunmen in Charlie Hebdo Attack Identified|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117063318/http://abcnews.go.com/International/gunmen-charlie-hebdo-attack-called-victims-names-shot/story?id=28050771|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2005年穆罕默德争议性漫画事件中心的丹麦，媒体机构的安保增加<ref name="rydermadi" />。

枪击案发生后数小时，西班牙内政大臣豪尔赫·费尔南德斯·迪亚兹表示，西班牙的反恐安保级别已经提升，该国将与法国共享袭击事件的有关信息，火车站周边等公共场所和全国各地城市的街道都增派警力<ref>{{cite news|title=In wake of Paris shooting, Spain worries about terror attacks on its home soil|url=http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/news/2015/01/08/in-wake-paris-shooting-spain-worries-about-terror-attacks-on-its-home-soil/|author=Andrew O'Reilly|publisher=[[Fox_News_Latino|Fox News Latino]]|date=2015-01-08|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110233048/http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/news/2015/01/08/in-wake-paris-shooting-spain-worries-about-terror-attacks-on-its-home-soil/|archive-date=2015-01-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

英国运输警察1月8日证实，将在伦敦[[圣潘克拉斯国际火车站|圣潘克拉斯国际火车站]]附近加强武装巡逻，有报告指出嫌疑人正移向[[欧洲之星|欧洲之星]]北部站点。他们表示，加强巡逻是对公众的保证和保持可见性，尤其是没有嫌疑人前往圣潘克拉斯的可靠报道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hamhigh.co.uk/news/armed_police_step_up_patrols_at_st_pancras_in_wake_of_charlie_hebdo_paris_massacre_1_3910282|title=Armed police step up patrols at St Pancras in wake of Charlie Hebdo Paris massacre|author=Paul Wright|work=Hampstead Highgate Express|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015170955/http://www.hamhigh.co.uk/news/armed_police_step_up_patrols_at_st_pancras_in_wake_of_charlie_hebdo_paris_massacre_1_3910282|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

